thread.title: Podcast: 'On Iowa' talks Iowa-Wisconsin showdown

title: Podcast: 'On Iowa' talks Iowa-Wisconsin showdown
text:
By Scott Dochterman and Marc Morehouse , The Gazette October 1, 2015 | 11:52 am 
The "On Iowa" podcast with Marc Morehouse and Scott Dochterman breaks down Saturday's Iowa-Wisconsin football showdown at Camp Randall Stadium and previews the rest of the Big Ten action. Marc and Scott also answer readers' Twitter questions. 
Click below to listen, or find this podcast on iTunes , Stitcher , and TuneIn .
